Well all,

I think that catches me up for the open links. Hopefully everyone is
enjoying the show. Feel free to give me any critiques you have on or
off list, I am open to your comments. For me I consider it my function
to keep everything fun and interesting.

Soon the great evil will be revealed and all this will come to an end.

I look foward to seeing what happens in 2012 and seeing you guys (and
gals) there.

See you soon.

- Preston

Oh, Airly, I have sent you some personal email about Hydras a couple
of times, have you received it?
